Hey People,

Today I have attended a session on Being “Successful with Freelancing”.

It was a great time with [Gaurav](https://www.linkedin.com/in/askgauravnanda/) and I really enjoyed every moment of it. This is the first time I attended the meetup on this topic.

I would like to share my takeaways from the session.

Without any delay, Lets Get Started

